data.description: Welcome to your charming new home! This adorable property greets you with an inviting open-concept layout & a convenient 2-car garage. The updated kitchen boasts new stainless steel appliances & a large stone sink, making meal preparation a breeze. Retreat to the master suite featuring double trey ceilings, a spacious walk-in closet, & a double vanity bathroom. Embrace eco-friendly living with solar panels ensuring energy savings year-round. Step outside to discover a tranquil goldfish pond, complementing the serene ambiance of the screened-in back patio. Nestled in the amenity-packed community of Rice Hope, residents have access to 3 lakes, a waterpark, swimming pool, playgrounds, parks, a dog park, & fitness center-ideal for families & active individuals alike. Enjoy the convenience of being within walking distance to 2 playgrounds, a dog park, fire pit, & soccer field. Located a short drive from historic Savannah & Pooler, this home offers the perfect blend of convenience & comfort.
